quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  68,0,Bismillaahir Rahmaanir Raheem
  68,1,Noon; walqalami wa maa yasturoon
  68,2,Maa anta bini'mati Rabbika bimajnoon
  68,3,Wa inna laka la ajran ghaira mamnoon
  68,4,Wa innaka la'alaa khuluqin 'azeem
  68,5,Fasatubsiru wa yubsiroon
  68,6,Bi ayyikumul maftoon
  68,7,Innaa Rabbaka Huwa a'lamu biman dalla 'an sabeelihee wa Huwa a'lamu bilmuhtadeen
  68,8,Falaa tuti'il mukazzibeen
  68,9,Waddoo law tudhinu fa-yudhinoon
  68,10,Wa laa tuti' kulla hallaa fim maheen
  68,11,Hammaazim mash shaaa'im binameem
  68,12,Mannaa'il lilkhairi mu'tadin aseem
  68,13,'Utullim ba'da zaalika zaneem
  68,14,An kaana zaa maalinw-wa baneen
  68,15,Izaa tutlaa 'alaihi aayaatunaa qaala asaateerul awwaleen
  68,16,Sanasimuhoo 'alal khurtoom
  68,17,Innaa balawnaahum kamaa balawnaaa As-haabal jannati iz 'aqsamoo la-yasri munnahaa musbiheen
  68,18,Wa laa yastasnoon
  68,19,Fataafa 'alaihaa taaa'i fum mir rabbika wa hum naaa'imoon
  68,20,Fa asbahat kassareem
  68,21,Fatanaadaw musbiheen
  68,22,Anighdoo 'alaa harsikum in kuntum saarimeen
  68,23,Fantalaqoo wa hum yatakhaafatoon
  68,24,Al laa yadkhulannahal yawma 'alaikum miskeen
  68,25,Wa ghadaw 'alaa hardin qaadireen
  68,26,Falammaa ra awhaa qaaloo
  68,27,Bal nahnu mahroomoon
  68,28,Qaala awsatuhum alam aqul lakum law laa tusabbihoon
  68,29,Qaaloo subhaana rabbinaaa innaa kunnaa zaalimeen
  68,30,Fa aqbala ba'duhum 'alaa ba'diny yatalaawamoon
  68,31,Qaaloo yaa wailanaaa innaa kunnaa taagheen
  68,32,'Asaa rabbunaaa any yubdilanaa khairam minhaaa innaaa ilaa rabbinaa raaghiboon
  68,33,"Kazaalikal azaab, wa la'azaabul aakhirati akbar; law kaanoo ya'lamoon"
  68,34,Inna lilmuttaqeena 'inda rabbihim jannaatin na'eem
  68,35,Afanaj'alul muslimeena kalmujrimeen
  68,36,Maa lakum kaifa tahhkumoon
  68,37,Am lakum kitaabun feehi tadrusoon
  68,38,Inna lakum feehi lamaa takhaiyaroon
  68,39,Am lakum aymaanun 'alainaa baalighatun ilaa yawmil qiyaamati inna lakum lamaa tahkumoon
  68,40,Salhum ayyuhum bizaa lika za'eem
  68,41,Am lahum shurakaaa'u falyaatoo bishurakaaa 'ihim in kaanoo saadiqeen
  68,42,Yawma yukshafu 'am saaqinw wa yud'awna ilas sujoodi falaa yastatee'oon
  68,43,Khaashi'atan absaaruhum tarhaquhum zillatunw wa qad kaanoo yud'awna ilassujoodi wa hum saalimoon
  68,44,Fazamee wa many yukazzibu bihaazal hadeesi sanastad rijuhum min haisu laa ya'lamoon
  68,45,Wa umlee lahum; inna kaidee mateen
  68,46,Am tas'aluhum ajran fahum mim maghramim musqaloon
  68,47,Am 'indahumul ghaibu fahum yaktuboon
  68,48,Fasbir lihkmi rabbika wa laa takun kasaahibil boot; iz naadaa wa huwa makzoom
  68,49,Law laaa an tadaara kahoo ni'matum mir rabbihee lanubiza bil'araaa'i wa huwa mazmoom
  68,50,Fajtabaahu rabbuhoo faja'alahoo minas saaliheen
  68,51,Wa iny-yakaadul lazeena kafaroo la-yuzliqoonaka biabsaarihim lammaa saml'uz-Zikra wa yaqooloona innahoo lamajnoon
  68,52,Wa maa huwa illaa zikrul lil'aalameen
